{"tid":1893640,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「受控」的不是疫情而是狗官 - 李碧華","createTime":"2020-02-23T11:41:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T16:17:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"27d01947eef0a02d2db6c0ea07461a1674b07b88","tid":1893640,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:41:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200222/20866791/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200222%2F20866791%2F&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyh1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=de93fab5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200222%2F20866791%2F&h=83c4b2fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200222/20866791/</a><br />\n<br />\n「受控」的不是疫情而是狗官 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200222/large/1582279545_710a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200222%2Flarge%2F1582279545_710a.jpg&h=bdd7d225&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在中國大陸，刻意隱瞞疫區接觸史、旅遊史&hellip;&hellip;隱瞞疫情致令肺炎病毒擴散不可收拾，這種行為不僅是道德問題，還是刑事問題，最高可判死刑！若是，像林鄭毒娥及一眾狗官庸官，早應人頭落地。<br />\n<br />\n尤其是庸劣無能之張建宗，長得像肥頭耷耳的巨嬰，實際上也是冇腦。此偽政務司司長出席立法會緊急質詢（毒娥當然不敢也不肯面對），表示「可能市民未必明白到，看不到有成績，但你們看到疫情現在受到控制&hellip;&hellip;」──真令人氣憤！全港市民不但看不到政府對防疫抗疫有何作為，更看不到疫情「受控」的任何理據。<br />\n<br />\n至今，毒娥仍未全面封關，所謂自我檢疫隔離14天又形同虛設，趴趴走的疑疫者抓到有處罰嗎？私自播毒害人不是重罪嗎？作為高官（第二把膠椅），為了什麼「使命」瞞疫？根據何栢良總監專業意見，疫情起碼14天（即潛伏期）內無新增感染個案才算受控。<span style=\"color: orange;\">何又坦言政府「未醒」，日日等病毒，不作為，「令人震驚」。</span><br />\n<br />\n天天大批大陸來客和150名單程證者入境，天天有確診個案，疫情受控？不失控已是奇蹟。所以低智廢噏坐享高薪人肉錄音「大家包容」者，別說做官，做人亦無意義。<br />\n<br />\n忠言逆耳，但上樑不正下樑歪，全「受控」充耳不聞，毀城滅代。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"726faba84fbbb51a65c873f1cf52979a1a6ad278","tid":1893640,"uid":262737,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:42:10.000Z","msg":"連登可否學會不要全篇貼？<br />\n貼少少貼link 得唔得？<br />\n記者要食飯，編輯要食飯。<br />\n唔好要人餓親得唔得？"},{"pid":"4fffe0de865aa8675741880fbe42e1bdd974ac6a","tid":1893640,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:47:07.000Z","msg":"直接聯署白宮要求youtube解釋點解限制言論自由<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-youtube-explain-why-youtubers-are-censored-or-no-ads-yellow-icons-coronavirus-topic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-youtube-explain-why-youtubers-are-censored-or-no-ads-yellow-icons-coronavirus-topic&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyh1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=b980c2b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-youtube-explain-why-youtubers-are-censored-or-no-ads-yellow-icons-coronavirus-topic</a>"},{"pid":"05d162828fda0dd8f32f6c85225a2e1943ae5d27","tid":1893640,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fffe0de865aa8675741880fbe42e1bdd974ac6a","tid":1893640,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:47:07.000Z","msg":"直接聯署白宮要求youtube解釋點解限制言論自由<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-youtube-explain-why-youtubers-are-censored-or-no-ads-yellow-icons-coronavirus-topic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-youtube-explain-why-youtubers-are-censored-or-no-ads-yellow-icons-coronavirus-topic&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyh1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=b980c2b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-youtube-explain-why-youtubers-are-censored-or-no-ads-yellow-icons-coronavirus-topic</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T16:17:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簽咗"}]}